WEBVTT

00:01.140 --> 00:01.300
Holiday!

00:01.500 --> 00:02.540
Holiday!

00:02.541 --> 00:03.619
Woo!

00:03.620 --> 00:04.618
Come with me.

00:04.619 --> 00:05.258
Where?

00:05.259 --> 00:06.338
Anywhere.

00:06.339 --> 00:07.218
Right now?

00:07.219 --> 00:08.300
Right now.

00:08.301 --> 00:11.099
Stop the car. Stop it!

00:11.100 --> 00:12.180
This is it!

00:13.220 --> 00:14.300
Grace.

00:16.820 --> 00:18.619
Grace woke up.

00:18.620 --> 00:20.739
Where is she then?
Zurich?

00:20.740 --> 00:22.180
I've got to find her.

00:22.181 --> 00:24.939
You awful, awful bastards.

00:24.940 --> 00:26.939
What the fuck has
happened to us all.

00:26.940 --> 00:27.940
'I love you, Rich.'

00:29.980 --> 00:31.900
She never woke up did
she from the accident?

00:31.901 --> 00:34.820
